data.name: FileStorm
data.description:
FileStorm claims to be a decentralized storage network built on top of IPFS protocol and MOAC Blockchain. It is claimed that with an original data verification consensus implemented with these two cutting edge technology, FileStorm is built to become next generation big data storing, processing and sharing platform, which is much more cost efficient than today’s cloud storage service.
